cooking_method:
1. Season chicken with salt and pepper. 
2. Grill chicken until cooked through. 
3. In a separate pan, melt butter and add minced garlic and rosemary. 
4. Squeeze lemon juice into butter mixture. 
5. Pour butter sauce over chicken and serve.

1. Heat oil in a wok or large skillet. 
2. Add vegetables and stir fry until tender. 
3. Add soy sauce and stir to combine. 
4. Serve over rice.

1. Cook spaghetti according to package instructions. 
2. In a separate pan, cook bacon until crispy. 
3. Whisk eggs and parmesan cheese together in a bowl. 
4. Drain spaghetti and add to bacon pan. 
5. Pour egg mixture over spaghetti and stir until eggs are cooked. 
6. Sprinkle black pepper on top and serve.
